<emphasis id="B919EACFED233847FEFBFAC1FD8CFAE8" box="[318,585,1295,1321]" italics="true" pageId="626" pageNumber="627">Phyllodelphys capensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A22A57B4ED233847FD93FAC1FCD1FAEB" box="[598,788,1295,1322]" pageId="626" pageNumber="627" rank="species">
<emphasis id="B919EACFED233847FD93FAC1FCCBFAE8" bold="true" box="[598,782,1295,1321]" pageId="626" pageNumber="627">gen. et sp. nov</emphasis>
.
</taxonomicNameLabel>
, female. A, labrum; B, mandibular palp; C, mandibular gnathobase; D, maxillule; E, maxilla; F, maxilliped. Scale bars: 0.02 mm.
</paragraph>
